Package: softbib
Type: Package
Title: Software Bibliographies for R Projects
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2022-01-16
Author: Vincent Arel-Bundock
Maintainer: Vincent Arel-Bundock <vincent.arel-bundock@umontreal.ca>
Description: This package detects all the `R` librairies used in a project and automatically creates software bibliographies in PDF, Word, Rmarkdown, and BibTeX formats.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
    checkmate,
    renv,
    rmarkdown,
    bibtex
License: GPL (>= 3)
Suggests: tinytest
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
